\section{Imports}

The runner depends on the interaction backends through callables.  That
keeps the production path interactive while leaving tests free to inject a
deterministic scripted shell or a fake editor session.

It also depends on a tutorial catalog, which keeps file loading and YAML
parsing out of the execution path itself.

